sentences.english: The Gang of Four Interpreter pattern is a special case. The definition is
sentences.chinese: 四人组解释器模式是一种特殊的情况。

sentences.english: An interpreter translates a program as it reads it, turning the program instructions, or code, directly into actions.
sentences.chinese: 解释器边读边翻译，将程序指令或代码直接实现。

sentences.english: They included a command-line interpreter and some small utility programs.
sentences.chinese: 还包括一个命令行解释器和一些小的实用程序。

sentences.english: Many of the examples in this book can be executed in the interpreter like this.
sentences.chinese: 这本书里的许多例子可以像这样在解释器里运行。

sentences.english: This interpreter uses the decorated style sheet tree to drive processing.
sentences.chinese: 该解释器使用装饰样式表树来驱动处理。

sentences.english: The completion mechanism might use the interpreter's symbol table.
sentences.chinese: 在完成机制可能使用解释器的符号表。

sentences.english: For example, this article describes the compiler and interpreter as separate functional components.
sentences.chinese: 例如，本文将编译器和解释器描述成单独的功能组件。

sentences.english: On traditional print maps, the legend serves as a translator for the symbols used.
sentences.chinese: 在传统的印刷地图中，图例是作为符号解释器使用的。

sentences.english: A kind of new method of software design based on command explainer model was put forward.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种新的基于命令解释器模型的软件设计方法。

sentences.english: This is what the interpreter sees. All right?
sentences.chinese: 这时解释器看到的，对吗？

sentences.english: Its interpreters are really fast and become faster.
sentences.chinese: 它的解释器真的很快，并且会变得更快。
